span class=\"a-size-base\">Keeps Beard Moisturized</span></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\"><span class=\"a-size-base\">Promotes Thicker Hair</span></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\"><span class=\"a-size-base\">Light, Citrus Mint Scent</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-11 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"ck1q0r-e0gyst-oy3f5f-s9rpb6\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-11\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container\" data-a-expander-name=\"aplus-module-expander\" data-a-expander-collapsed-height=\"360\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-spacing apm-floatnone apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-sidemodule aplus-module-content\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-hero-image\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/a8b54f95-916c-45da-ae10-ff0a3f6bcc84.__CR0,0,970,300_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Scumbassador Tip - Tip for using REUZEL 3-in-1 Tea Tree Shampoo\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/a8b54f95-916c-45da-ae10-ff0a3f6bcc84.__CR0,0,970,300_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"apm-heromodule-textright apm-hero-text\">\r\n<h3>SCUMBASSADOR TIP:</h3>\r\nWash your beard with REFRESH first before doing a beard trim.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-5 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"ynqooz-1bzbgm-7vikeg-fh5a5e\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-5\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing aplus-module-content\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-tablemodule\">\r\n<table class=\"apm-tablemodule-table\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbo