ser habits and environmental factors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">Self-Cleaning. With a self-cleaning design, the Empty Wash Fill dock cleans itself, too, For even easier maintenance. As the mop cleaning roller moves, it also pushes dirty water into the drain, where it can be pulled into the dirty water tank.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-4 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"7bmoc2-akbbip-vpwl97-xukqzq\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-4\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container\" data-a-expander-name=\"aplus-module-expander\" data-a-expander-collapsed-height=\"700\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-floatleft apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<table class=\"apm-fixed-width apm-fourthcol-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/dcc534d4-a557-4815-817e-2dc8c65a42f9.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"self emptying\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/dcc534d4-a557-4815-817e-2dc8c65a42f9.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/feea8fff-cb7d-4777-9c1f-e35bd68f6999.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"self cleaning\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/feea8fff-cb7d-4777-9c1f-e35bd68f6999.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/d206ce4f-fbac-4580-966f-2a2c09e76c69.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Cliff edge sensor\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/d206ce4f-fbac-4580-966f-2a2c09e76c69.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/b1f8f18e-93b8-45aa-907e-4e56e2641341.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"robot vacuum mop\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/b1f8f18e-93b8-45aa-907e-4e56e2641341.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Self Emptying</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">3 L dust bag is enough to make it collecting dust</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">for 60 days real hands-free throughout the process.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Self-Cleaning</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Mop can be washed back to the base station, and can set how often to clean. Always carry a clean mop for cleaning.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Zero Attention Needed</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">EVA uses drop-sensing technology to avoid falling down stairs and off of ledges.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Intelligent Cleaning Path</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Customizes your cleaning with room-by-room. Intelligently plan the route to avoid repeated cleaning and clean your room most effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-4 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"aavgyq-oobc3b-qdbgat-qzewum\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-4\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container\" data-a-expander-name=\"aplus-module-expander\" data-a-expander-collapsed-height=\"700\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-floatleft apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<table class=\"apm-fixed-width apm-fourthcol-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/5bacde1b-6429-4f8f-bcea-c5486af2cb21.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"power section\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/5bacde1b-6429-4f8f-bcea-c5486af2cb21.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/215c597e-230f-4256-ae42-e4fc8c1cc3ae.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"moping self\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/215c597e-230f-4256-ae42-e4fc8c1cc3ae.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/64303aa0-8e26-425a-ba73-93f554953e89.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Smart environment perception\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/64303aa0-8e26-425a-ba73-93f554953e89.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/4454dc96-c097-4baf-ac12-f600cb4e45f1.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"over-obstacle capacity\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/4454dc96-c097-4baf-ac12-f600cb4e45f1.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Strong Suction for Deep Cleaning</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Easily picks up debris, pet hair and dirt from every corner and automatically boosts power when vacuuming on carpets, while still maintaining tolerable low-noise level.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Mop Rotary Scrubbing Cleaning</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">The 4-inch large high-speed spin mop 180rpm maximum cleaning efficienc. 12N continuous downward pressure. Easy to clean dust, dander, juice stains, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Obstacle Avoidance Technology</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Smart environment perception. Can actively avoid objects taller than 3 inches. Automatically identify and recognize common household obstacles and furniture, even in the dark.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Obstacle Crossing Ability</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Overcome 0.8inch obstacles easily, even thresholds can\'t stop me. Free room to clean between.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-b