cel-widget=\"aplus-3p-module-b\" data-csa-c-id=\"5se8p9-2cwtz4-dwkk9x-9xtz5g\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper aplus-3p-fixed-width\"><img class=\"a-spacing-base\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/ABIY41HTAB3PA/35943d80-b8c0-4406-aa5b-f23f085c1cb2.__CR1,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"2\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/ABIY41HTAB3PA/35943d80-b8c0-4406-aa5b-f23f085c1cb2.__CR1,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-b aplus-standard\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-3p-module-b\" data-csa-c-id=\"gkf9zq-bo6c10-w03inv-x6be01\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper aplus-3p-fixed-width\"><img class=\"a-spacing-base\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/ABIY41HTAB3PA/ebec1206-1424-4b6f-87e4-adf72ec1b850.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"3\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/ABIY41HTAB3PA/ebec1206-1424-4b6f-87e4-adf72ec1b850.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">AUVON</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">Live Smart, Live Healthy</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">AUVON TENS Unit</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">The TENS machine is safe, non-invasive, drug free method of pain relief and pain management. Many people have even used it for intense pain from sports injury, knee injury, foot, hip, arthritis or tennis elbow.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">Get rid of Further Pain from Installment</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">Compared to the button-style electrodes and lead wires, 2mm pin plug electrodes patches and lead wires are easier to be connected or detached without any further pain from installment even when the electrodes pads are on your body.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">Compact and Lightweight</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">Packing enough power to thoroughly use low frequency electrical muscle stimulation to massage your body, it fits in your briefcase or purse to take on the go, whether out for gym, trip, office, groceries, you can travel calmly knowing pain relief is there.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">Maintenance and Care</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">1. When you are finished using the TENS device, turn it off and take off the pads. Store the unit in a cool,dry place until next use.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">2. After usage, please cover the pads with the included pads holders / protective film and put them back in the included pouch. Applying a few drops water before and after usage will increase the longevity of the pads. 3. Charge the unit at least every</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">3 month in event it is not used regularly. You can also charge the unit with the included wall charger or directly from your computer using the included USB cable.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">SAFETY PRECAUTIONS AND WARNINGS</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">If you have one of the following conditions, please read AUVON Muscle Stimulator USER MANUAL carefully or consult with your physician before purchasing or using this device (e.g. any acute disease; tumor; infectious disease; pregnant; heart disease; high fever; abnormal blood pressure; lack of skin sensation or an abnormal skin condition; any condition requiring the active supervision of a physician.)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-5 aplus-standard\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-5\" data-csa-c-id=\"bapgh2-9xobgb-sc3tb8-55m3bm\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing aplus-module-content\">\r\n