\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/52ae1f40-f83a-4583-8c19-4c38c442f285.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"robotic pool cleaner\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/52ae1f40-f83a-4583-8c19-4c38c442f285.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Powerful Cleaning</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">With <span class=\"a-text-bold\">2pcs upgraded </span>powerful, yet <span class=\"a-text-bold\">efficient motors</span>, this automatic pool cleaner can provide a deep clean, attacking and removing the dirt with ease, ensuring a clean pool for you and your families.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Always Ready to Clean</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Built-in 2600mAh lithium battery to run for up to 50 minutes before recharging. This cordless robotic pool cleaner only takes around<span class=\"a-text-bold\"> 3-4 hours for fully charged </span>while others need 7-8 hours. Power off the cleaner before charging.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Agile &amp; Rapid Cleaning</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">With moving speed approximately <span class=\"a-text-bold\">16meter/min</span>, this intelligent pool vacuum rapidly cleans all sorts of dirt &amp; debris in your 50㎡pool in around 50 minutes, save you time and energy.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Superior Filtration System</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">This pool vacuum automatic also <span class=\"a-text-bold\">improve water circulation</span> and act as a second filter to your pool. 2 suction doors help to suck fine dust particles and rough debris into the filter tray that can filter the water down to 2 microns for a really clean pool.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-4 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"p5ez0a-3l61un-vfkjrb-yc8bgx\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-4\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container\" data-a-expander-name=\"aplus-module-expander\" data-a-expander-collapsed-height=\"700\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-floatleft apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-spacing\">\r\n<table class=\"apm-fixed-width apm-fourthcol-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/427acf87-5b76-4e3a-ad66-827fa1e27511.__CR0,0,600,600_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"1\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/427acf87-5b76-4e3a-ad66-827fa1e27511.__CR0,0,600,600_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/84db5e76-7243-4d8c-8aac-105d73dec409.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"pool cleaner robot\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/84db5e76-7243-4d8c-8aac-105d73dec409.__CR0,0,220,220_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/b2faae44-0877-478a-9959-756b09ae502b.__CR0,0,300,300_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"1\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/b2faae44-0877-478a-9959-756b09ae502b.__CR0,0,300,300_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n<th class=\"apm-center\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/9233a979-bb3e-4042-9d59-896ab43cdcb1.__CR0,0,1600,1600_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"1\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/9233a979-bb3e-4042-9d59-896ab43cdcb1.__CR0,0,1600,1600_PT0_SX220_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n\r\n</div></th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Touch &amp; Reserve Technology</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">It will <span class=\"a-text-bold\">automatically reverse </span>when it touches the wall. Will also stop running and automatically dock when run out of power. The buzzer will be alarming when lifting out of the pool. Press the switch to OFF and the cleaner will be shut down.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Easy to Clean the Filter Tray</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">The<span class=\"a-text-bold\"> filter is big enough</span> for normal cleaning, it traps and locks-in all sorts of dirt &amp; debris. Also very easy to pop out &amp; clean.Take off the filter tray and use a water pipe to clean it. Definitely save your time.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Always Easy to Handle</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">This pool cleaners vacuum is the <span class=\"a-text-bold\">lightest model</span> in the market and you can easily remove from the pool, the package comes with a retriveing hook to pull out the cordless pool cleaner without going into the pool after completing the working cycle.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"apm-top\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-fourthcol\">\r\n<h4 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Fit Flat Bottom Pools</h4>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">This Pool Cleaner is perfect for above-gorund pools( up to 30\' diameter), and IN-GROUND flat bottom pools (ONLY ONE DEPTH, up to 15\' X 35\').</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">No pulsating hoses or pumps, for a peaceful pool environment.</p>\r\n<p class=\"a-size-small\">Note: Only works for flat pools.</p>\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module module-12 aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"4qu5zc-2x2mgx-fqja2h-ik7cio\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-module-12\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container\" data-a-expander-name=\"aplus-module-expander\" data-a-expander-collapsed-height=\"360\">\r\n<div class=\"a-expander-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper apm-spacing apm-floatnone apm-fixed-width\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-sidemodule aplus-module-content\">\r\n<div class=\"apm-hero-image\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/a9a8e5cf-11d7-42c0-b346-89144f54e9ee.__CR0,0,970,300_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"automatic pool vacuum\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/a9a8e5cf-11d7-42c0-b346-89144f54e9ee.__CR0,0,970,300_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-b aplus-standard\" data-csa-c-id=\"fe03s-f6nfo6-gf2q5l-jkt9cl\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-3p-module-b\">\r\n<div class=\"aplus-module-wrapper aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\">Ideal for Residential Flat Bottom Pools of All Shapes.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"a-spacing-base\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/764f136f-0857-4acf-a597-efa3cfb7386e.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"7\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/sc/764f136f-0857-4acf-a597-efa3cfb7386e.__CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" />\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">For Optimal Use:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Use on flat floor pool, especially on above ground swimming pool. Not suitable for very large in-ground pools.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Not able to climb walls or stairs, and also not good for cleaning algae.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\">Note:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">After each use, wipe-dry the charging pin with a paper towel or cotton swab, and wait a few minutes to let the moisture dry out before charging.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Do not operate the cleaner when there are people in the pool.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">Always remember to turn off the power switch when the cleaner is not in the water to protect the battery and the motor.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">The cleaner should be stored in a cool place when charging, and not covered with anything to prevent the damage of internal electrical components caused by overheating.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"a-spacing-base\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\"><span class=\"a-text-italic\">Let AIPER automated cleaning system do the dirty work for you ! Your AIPER is designed to handle all the work and worries so you can enjoy your pool more with your families.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"aplusSustainabilityStory-2_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"aplusSustainabilityStory-2\" data-csa-c-id=\"kpzssz-f94ayy-cwh2zh-6gwa8w\"