lus-media/vc/6acee921-e984-4e70-9abf-2261aa077413.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Wi-Fi Repeater to Boost your Coverage\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/6acee921-e984-4e70-9abf-2261aa077413.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-text-center\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module premium-module-2-fullbackground-image aplus-premium\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-premium-module-2-fullbackground-image\" data-csa-c-id=\"11sezl-jakt2a-ybw0vk-z5h474\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus premium-aplus-module-2\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-background-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none background-image\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/3ec52101-17b4-4076-a0f2-43ad7b387a5a.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"OneMesh WiFi Extender\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/3ec52101-17b4-4076-a0f2-43ad7b387a5a.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-text-center\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module premium-module-2-fullbackground-image aplus-premium\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-premium-module-2-fullbackground-image\" data-csa-c-id=\"es3hb6-6ad9vp-uqwwo5-sdwh8e\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus premium-aplus-module-2\">\r\n<h1 class=\"a-text-center aplus-container-3 aplus-h1 a-text-bold\">OneMesh For Seamless Whole-Home Streaming</h1>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-background-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none background-image\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/3fa5cb84-f095-49ec-bc5f-f620af1cdc8e.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Seamless Whole Home Streaming\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/3fa5cb84-f095-49ec-bc5f-f620af1cdc8e.__CR0,0,1464,600_PT0_SX1464_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-text-center\">\r\n<p class=\"aplus-description aplus-container-3 aplus-p1\">With TP-Link OneMesh technology effortlessly create a Mesh network with a single network name for uninterrupted streaming when moving around your home. Just connect the RE550 range extender to a OneMesh router for a smart roaming experience that can be managed from the TP-Link Tether app.[2]</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module premium-module-4-two-column-images aplus-premium\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-premium-module-4-two-column-images\" data-csa-c-id=\"w63xmw-80hcz1-7op04p-5i4j6y\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus premium-aplus-module-4 aplus-container-1\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-two-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none {\'column-image\'}\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/b0ecbd98-7774-4e48-a961-8b87c605949e.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"High Performance Dual Band Wireless up to 1900 Mbps\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/b0ecbd98-7774-4e48-a961-8b87c605949e.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-heading\">\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h3 a-text-bold\">High Performance Dual-Band Wi-Fi up to 1900 Mbps</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-description\">\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p3\">Supporting the 802.11ac Wi-Fi standard, 3x faster than standard 802.11n speeds, the RE550 delivers up to 1900Mbps of fast speeds for bandwidth-intensive tasks like 4K streaming, online gaming, video calls and more.¹</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none {\'column-image\'}\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/5d69f6f4-f817-4e80-9679-2d94c5c71e77.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"Built-in Access Point Mode\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/5d69f6f4-f817-4e80-9679-2d94c5c71e77.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-heading\">\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h3 a-text-bold\">Built-in Access Point Mode</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-description\">\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p3\">The RE550 is more than a wireless range externder. With a built-in Access Point mode for plug in an Ethernet cable into the Ethernet port to easily turn any wired connection into a high-speed 3x3 MIMO dual-band Wi-Fi signal.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module premium-module-4-two-column-images aplus-premium\" data-cel-widget=\"aplus-premium-module-4-two-column-images\" data-csa-c-id=\"5qedhi-213qwx-11o3bz-74fk5h\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus premium-aplus-module-4 aplus-container-1\">\r\n<h1 class=\"a-text-center premium-module-4-heading aplus-h1 a-text-bold\">Setup Made Easy</h1>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-two-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none {\'column-image\'}\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/c573c392-252d-4e0c-bccd-57b1815acec0.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"tp-link wifi range extender\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media-library-service-media/c573c392-252d-4e0c-bccd-57b1815acec0.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-heading\">\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h3 a-text-bold\">Always Find the Best Location for Placement</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-description\">\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p3\">The intelligent signal indicator helps you easily find the best place to position your RE550 for optimal signal strength from your existing router to boost WiFi coverage.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none premium-aplus-column\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none {\'column-image\'}\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/578f69a9-085c-40a2-b5f2-3d22cb14d920.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" alt=\"TP-Link\" data-src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-media/vc/578f69a9-085c-40a2-b5f2-3d22cb14d920.__CR0,0,650,350_PT0_SX650_V1___.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-heading\">\r\n<h1 class=\"aplus-h3 a-text-bold\">Control At Your Fingertips</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none column-description\">\r\n<p class=\"aplus-p3\">Set up and manage your Wi-Fi network through the TP-Link Tether app from your Android or iOS mobile device. Maintain full control of your network even when you\'re away from the house.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"va-related-videos-widget_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget pd_rd_w-qTty9 pd_rd_r-T7X7CE1B3M0YTDYM52A8 pd_rd_wg-YZGLz\" data-feature-name=\"va-related-videos-widget\" data-cel-widget=\"va-related-videos-widget_feature_div\" data-csa-c-id=\"u5fje5-o45vt3-mu6rwv-wpj3dw\">\r\n<div class=\"a-section vse-vwdp-video-block-wrapper\" data-csa-c-component=\"vse-video-widget-detail-page\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"vse-video-widget-detail-page\" data-csa-c-cs-type=\"vse\" data-csa-c-painter=\"va-related-videos-widget\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"btf.vse\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-id=\"8i7ic3-wex5fo-cj5yts-7s5x83\">\r\n<div id=\"rvs-vse-related-videos\" class=\"a-section vse-carousel-container\">\r\n<div id=\"rvs-related-videos-9dde2956-96c4-4c2e-93b4-50a6cc0cc047-vse_vwdp_ingress\" class=\"a-begin a-carousel-container a-carousel-display-st